    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Receiving rights of tenancy or custody and use of an object or land from its owner in return for payment. The terms of such arrangements are generally set forth in a lease. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
